qas.question: What are the main coastal towns

answers.text: Minehead, Watchet, Burnham-on-Sea, Weston-super-Mare, Clevedon and Portishead

qas.question: what is the name of the natural reserve area

answers.text: Bridgwater Bay, and is a National Nature Reserve

qas.question: what does the western coastline look like

answers.text: the coastline is high and dramatic where the plateau of Exmoor meets the sea, with high cliffs and waterfalls.
